message.content: cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SI. The paper describes a task related to community question answering, which involves natural language processing and information retrieval techniques. Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval) are the most likely sub-categories. Additionally, the task involves similarity and duplicate detection, which are common topics in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Learning). Finally, the use of StackExchange subforums suggests a possible connection to cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
